1
00:00:00,840 --> 00:00:03,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Excuse me, you dropped this.</i></font>

2
00:00:04,280 --> 00:00:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sorry...</i></font>

3
00:00:08,700 --> 00:00:10,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Namie-chan...</i></font>

4
00:00:20,140 --> 00:00:21,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why?</i></font>

5
00:00:21,370 --> 00:00:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Satoru-kun?</i></font>

6
00:00:22,430 --> 00:00:24,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why didn't you come that day?</i></font>

7
00:00:24,850 --> 00:00:25,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Because...</i></font>

8
00:00:26,100 --> 00:00:28,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I waited for so long...</i></font>

9
00:00:28,090 --> 00:00:30,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mean I... I also wanted to...</i></font>

10
00:00:32,920 --> 00:00:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Namie-chan!</i></font>

11
00:00:34,120 --> 00:00:35,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Satoru-kun!</i></font>

12
00:00:35,380 --> 00:00:36,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Goddess!</font>

13
00:00:37,480 --> 00:00:39,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? What are you doing?</font>

14
00:00:39,210 --> 00:00:41,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let us hold one another, Namie-chan!</i></font>

15
00:00:41,830 --> 00:00:44,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let us hold one another, Satoru-kun!</i></font>

16
00:00:44,850 --> 00:00:47,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, we must hold one another!</font>

17
00:00:52,150 --> 00:00:53,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now...</font>

18
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:56,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now...</font>

19
00:01:00,740 --> 00:01:01,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now...</font>

20
00:01:05,350 --> 00:01:10,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... is this a trap?</font>

21
00:01:10,420 --> 00:01:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

22
00:01:11,750 --> 00:01:16,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time I thought I 
would be more "dere."</font>

23
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:22,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now...</font>

24
00:01:23,290 --> 00:01:25,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's gotten into you?!</font>

25
00:01:25,150 --> 00:01:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When one has been a reincarnation 
goddess for so long,</font>

26
00:01:29,420 --> 00:01:32,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they sometimes get a sudden desire to
feel another's touch: a fit, if you will.</font>

27
00:01:32,650 --> 00:01:34,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A fit?!</font>

28
00:01:35,930 --> 00:01:36,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now...</font>

29
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:40,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold me close.</font>

30
00:01:59,830 --> 00:02:02,500
<font size="20">{\an1}<font size="18"><b><font color="#7c4430"><font color="#45230c">My Ribdiculous Reincarnation</font></font></b></font></font>

31
00:01:59,830 --> 00:02:02,500
<font size="20">{\an1}<font size="18"><b><font color="#7c4430"><font color="#45230c">My Ribdiculous Reincarnation</font></font></b></font></font>

32
00:03:12,130 --> 00:03:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go.</font>

33
00:03:13,930 --> 00:03:14,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this?</font>

34
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A yellowtail fish.</font>

35
00:03:15,690 --> 00:03:17,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's great wrapped in kombu.</font>

36
00:03:17,230 --> 00:03:20,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't wrap me in kombu. 
Hold me tight and close.</font>

37
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll tighten my necktie!</font>

38
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:22,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do that.</font>

39
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:24,180
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#e16ba5">Ca<font color="#ecb373">nd<font color="#99dd7a">y<font color="#77d8d2"> Fair</font></font></font></font></b></font></font>

40
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:24,180
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#e16ba5">Ca<font color="#ecb373">nd<font color="#99dd7a">y<font color="#77d8d2"> Fair</font></font></font></font></b></font></font>

41
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:24,180
<font size="20"><font size="12"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#4b413b">Buy one participating sweet</font></b></font></font></font>

42
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:24,180
<font size="20"><font size="8"><b><font color="#d6251d">Get one</font></b></font></font>

43
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:24,180
<font size="20"><font size="12"><b><font color="#d6251d">Free!</font></b></font></font>

44
00:03:22,570 --> 00:03:23,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Close the register...</font>

45
00:03:23,330 --> 00:03:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do that.</font>

46
00:03:24,190 --> 00:03:25,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have some rice porridge.</font>

47
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't end our meal with that.</font>

48
00:03:26,310 --> 00:03:28,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like to end my 
meal with udon noodles.</font>

49
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh no!</font>

50
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't do enough research!</font>

51
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

52
00:03:33,940 --> 00:03:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is what you wanted, right?</font>

53
00:03:36,460 --> 00:03:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, hold me tight.</font>

54
00:03:41,580 --> 00:03:42,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

55
00:03:45,790 --> 00:03:48,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure I could have a 
lot of fun right now...</font>

56
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:49,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

57
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm scared of what comes after!</font>

58
00:03:52,870 --> 00:03:54,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't deny that you should be.</font>

59
00:03:54,670 --> 00:03:57,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really wish you would!</font>

60
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry.</font>

61
00:03:59,050 --> 00:04:02,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Afterwards, the overwhelming
humiliation and regret I feel</font>

62
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:07,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will make me kill you until you forget.</font>

63
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is getting worse than "scary"!</font>

64
00:04:11,290 --> 00:04:13,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to reincarnate, fast!</font>

65
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:21,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you get?</font>

66
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:21,740
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#000602"><font size="9">Vegetable</font></font></b></font></font>

67
00:04:21,740 --> 00:04:23,340
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#000602"><font size="32">Vegetable</font></font></b></font></font>

68
00:04:22,210 --> 00:04:23,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vegetable!</font>

69
00:04:24,090 --> 00:04:29,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, a world where you are an edible 
vegetable is a terrifying thought.</font>

70
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great. That keeps us on theme.</font>

71
00:04:35,270 --> 00:04:38,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, what's going on here?</font>

72
00:04:38,730 --> 00:04:41,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold me before you reincarnate.</font>

73
00:04:41,590 --> 00:04:46,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'll...</font>

74
00:04:46,590 --> 00:04:50,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">pass!</font>

75
00:04:57,020 --> 00:04:59,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel... lonely...</font>

76
00:05:05,930 --> 00:05:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm back!</font>

77
00:05:08,610 --> 00:05:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And of course, you return.</font>

78
00:05:10,570 --> 00:05:12,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is your fit over?</font>

79
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:15,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I apologize for making you worry.</font>

80
00:05:17,650 --> 00:05:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not over.</font>

81
00:05:20,790 --> 00:05:23,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, let's hear your report.</font>

82
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll stick it in myself!</font>

83
00:05:28,050 --> 00:05:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Shine!</font>

84
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wanted to be the one to stick it in.</i></font>

85
00:05:31,020 --> 00:05:33,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe some other time.</i></font>

86
00:05:34,330 --> 00:05:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was the tomato hero!</i></font>

87
00:05:36,110 --> 00:05:38,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A very ripe tomato, I see.</i></font>

88
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:43,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I rose up to fight the Demon 
King who threatened the world!</i></font>

89
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:44,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The time is ripe!</font>

90
00:05:44,420 --> 00:05:46,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yes, it is.</i></font>

91
00:05:46,580 --> 00:05:49,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will be the tomato that saves the world!</font>

92
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will!</font>

93
00:05:51,730 --> 00:05:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were aggressive from 
the start this time.</font>

94
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:56,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I was just a single tomato.</font>

95
00:05:56,590 --> 00:05:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I started by gathering allies!</font>

96
00:05:59,380 --> 00:06:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Twinkle twinkle!</font>

97
00:06:03,050 --> 00:06:07,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey, won't anyone come with 
me to beat the Demon King?</font>

98
00:06:06,380 --> 00:06:07,980
<font size="20"><font color="#bc8ac0"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS">Big Sky Veggies</font></b></font></font>

99
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello? Anybody?</font>

100
00:06:11,470 --> 00:06:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But nobody answered!</font>

101
00:06:13,900 --> 00:06:15,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were a vegetable, after all.</font>

102
00:06:15,470 --> 00:06:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello? Anybody?</font>

103
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:21,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Who's there? Who's there?</font>

104
00:06:19,430 --> 00:06:24,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I shouted as loudly as I could, but only 
the old man on guard duty heard me.</i></font>

105
00:06:26,210 --> 00:06:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is just a horror story.</i></font>

106
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My wife! It's my dead wife!</font>

107
00:06:31,030 --> 00:06:35,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I got the old man to join my party...</i></font>

108
00:06:35,780 --> 00:06:36,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Stop.</i></font>

109
00:06:37,580 --> 00:06:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How?</font>

110
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you know...</font>

111
00:06:39,950 --> 00:06:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a lovable guy!</font>

112
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:44,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Share some of that love with me.</font>

113
00:06:44,460 --> 00:06:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no, no, no, no, no, no...</font>

114
00:06:46,460 --> 00:06:50,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But having an old guy in the party was 
bad from a visual design standpoint...</i></font>

115
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hot Old Man Magic!</font>

116
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:56,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hot Old Man Onion!</font>

117
00:06:56,060 --> 00:06:58,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a brutal thing to do to someone.</font>

118
00:06:59,150 --> 00:07:02,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And that was the birth of Onion Warrior!</i></font>

119
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:03,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}O-Onion! Onion!</font>

120
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His special ability was making people cry.</i></font>

121
00:07:04,210 --> 00:07:05,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm from Awaji!</font>

122
00:07:05,420 --> 00:07:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure he wanted to cry 
about what happened to him.</font>

123
00:07:07,690 --> 00:07:10,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that onion is...</font>

124
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:10,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here!</font>

125
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:11,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm from Awaji!</font>

126
00:07:11,860 --> 00:07:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You brought him back as a gift?</font>

127
00:07:14,290 --> 00:07:16,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is he edible?</font>

128
00:07:16,370 --> 00:07:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our first enemy was the cook!</font>

129
00:07:16,980 --> 00:07:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm from Awaji! I'm from Awaji!</font>

130
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:22,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd say I'm surprised,
but somehow I'm really not.</i></font>

131
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it, you!</font>

132
00:07:24,170 --> 00:07:25,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run!</font>

133
00:07:25,290 --> 00:07:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll cook you, boil you, 
throw you in a pot!</font>

134
00:07:29,460 --> 00:07:30,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oops!</font>

135
00:07:32,410 --> 00:07:34,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The security guard!</font>

136
00:07:36,570 --> 00:07:38,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, boo!</font>

137
00:07:39,010 --> 00:07:41,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hot Old Man Eggplant Magic!</font>

138
00:07:41,250 --> 00:07:44,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I quickly sealed his soul 
inside the nearest vegetable.</font>

139
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:48,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chef!</font>

140
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time, you were the enemy of humanity.</font>

141
00:07:51,100 --> 00:07:54,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure he never imagined that he'd 
be the one to end up on the menu.</font>

142
00:07:54,910 --> 00:07:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that eggplant...</font>

143
00:07:56,850 --> 00:07:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is right here!</font>

144
00:07:58,410 --> 00:07:59,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Another gift.</font>

145
00:07:59,730 --> 00:08:01,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And only half of him?</font>

146
00:08:01,170 --> 00:08:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, I'll skip the details, but...</font>

147
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:05,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cilantro Knight!</font>

148
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:05,190
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Cilantro Knight</b></font></font>

149
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:05,190
<font size="20"><font size="15">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Strength</b></font></font></font>

150
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:05,190
<font size="20"><font size="15">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Deliciousness</b></font></font></font>

151
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:05,190
<font size="20"><font size="13">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Nutritional Value</b></font></font></font>

152
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:05,190
<font size="20"><font size="13">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Some like him, some don't</b></font></font></font>

153
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cucumber Samurai!</font>

154
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,500
<font size="20"><font size="21"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Cucumber Samurai</b></font></font></font>

155
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,500
<font size="20"><font size="16">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Strength</b></font></font></font>

156
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,500
<font size="20"><font size="16">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Deliciousness</b></font></font></font>

157
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,500
<font size="20"><font size="14">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Nutritional Value</b></font></font></font>

158
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,500
<font size="20"><font size="14">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Great with miso, milord</b></font></font></font>

159
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:08,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Cabbage Gladiator...</font>

160
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:08,000
<font size="20"><font size="22"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Cabbage Gladiator</b></font></font></font>

161
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:08,000
<font size="20"><font size="17">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Strength</b></font></font></font>

162
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:08,000
<font size="20"><font size="17">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Deliciousness</b></font></font></font>

163
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:08,000
<font size="20"><font size="15">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Nutritional Value</b></font></font></font>

164
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:08,000
<font size="20"><font size="15">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Friend to caterpillars</b></font></font></font>

165
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>all joined my party!</i></font>

166
00:08:09,530 --> 00:08:11,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The party seems unbalanced, job-wise.</font>

167
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:16,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just so you know, all these vegetables 
were once my party members!</font>

168
00:08:16,010 --> 00:08:17,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are they edible?</font>

169
00:08:17,510 --> 00:08:19,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you <i>sure</i> they're edible?</font>

170
00:08:19,970 --> 00:08:22,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And did you really need such a big party?</font>

171
00:08:21,790 --> 00:08:23,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hoy, hoy, hoy, hoy!</font>

172
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:24,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vegetables, hey!</font>

173
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:28,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hoy, hoy, hoy, hoy! Vegetables, hey!</font>

174
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:29,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hoy, hoy, hoy, hoy!</font>

175
00:08:29,730 --> 00:08:31,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vegetables, hey!</font>

176
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cucumber!</font>

177
00:08:34,020 --> 00:08:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In death, a cucumber I remain!</font>

178
00:08:37,070 --> 00:08:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cabbage!</font>

179
00:08:41,410 --> 00:08:43,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cilantro!</font>

180
00:08:43,910 --> 00:08:48,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A lot of my companions got 
eaten and died on the way,</font>

181
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I had no choice but to recruit more.</font>

182
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:52,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to be a monster</font>

183
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:54,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to eat some veggies you 
find on the roadside.</font>

184
00:08:54,500 --> 00:08:57,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, by the time I made 
it to the Demon King's castle,</font>

185
00:08:57,550 --> 00:09:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>there were only four of us left.</i></font>

186
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:04,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If anything, I'm shocked 
you made it there.</i></font>

187
00:09:04,510 --> 00:09:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My party consisted of...</font>

188
00:09:06,060 --> 00:09:07,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onion Warrior!</font>

189
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm from Awaji!</font>

190
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:10,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm shocked the security guard 
actually made it that far.</font>

191
00:09:10,070 --> 00:09:12,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tofu Martial Artist, who joined halfway.</font>

192
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It feels like he'd crumble 
apart if you hit him.</font>

193
00:09:14,660 --> 00:09:16,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And finally...</font>

194
00:09:16,820 --> 00:09:18,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Evil Dragon God Bahalmetia!</font>

195
00:09:18,780 --> 00:09:20,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That one, I did not see coming.</i></font>

196
00:09:20,380 --> 00:09:26,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It explains how you made it to the 
Demon King's castle, at least.</i></font>

197
00:09:26,430 --> 00:09:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>By the way,</i></font>

198
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Evil Dragon God Bahalmetia</font>

199
00:09:29,290 --> 00:09:32,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was actually the weakest 
member of the party!</font>

200
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:36,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weaker than the onion who was 
once a night security guard?</font>

201
00:09:36,370 --> 00:09:38,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Evil Dragon God Bahalmetia's level was...</font>

202
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">72.</font>

203
00:09:40,300 --> 00:09:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Onion Warrior was Level 98!</font>

204
00:09:41,540 --> 00:09:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'm from Awaji!</i></font>

205
00:09:43,170 --> 00:09:46,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, the max level 
for that world was 99!</font>

206
00:09:46,490 --> 00:09:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see the night security 
guy was an XP grinder.</font>

207
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:51,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tofu Martial Artist was 92.</font>

208
00:09:52,260 --> 00:09:53,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you?</font>

209
00:09:53,780 --> 00:09:55,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">872.</font>

210
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:58,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You added a limit-breaking option 
when I wasn't looking, didn't you?</font>

211
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, even if a vegetable hits the 
level cap, it's still a vegetable.</font>

212
00:10:03,410 --> 00:10:05,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you explain why a Level 98 onion</font>

213
00:10:05,340 --> 00:10:08,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was stronger than the 
Evil Dragon God, then?</font>

214
00:10:14,090 --> 00:10:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The last battle with the Demon King, 
Potato Warrior, was about to begin!</i></font>

215
00:10:19,420 --> 00:10:20,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Another warrior.</font>

216
00:10:21,390 --> 00:10:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To think the friendly guy we met at 
the bar was actually the Demon King!</i></font>

217
00:10:21,450 --> 00:10:23,890
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#1d201d">Bar
No Demons</font></b></font></font>

218
00:10:25,250 --> 00:10:27,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even I didn't see that coming!</i></font>

219
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, that is clearly the Demon King.</i></font>

220
00:10:35,660 --> 00:10:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hot Old Man Magic!</font>

221
00:10:36,830 --> 00:10:39,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The real surprise for me was that 
you met the Demon King at a bar,</font>

222
00:10:39,390 --> 00:10:43,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">became his friend, then ripped out his 
soul and sealed it inside a vegetable.</font>

223
00:10:44,540 --> 00:10:46,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll get you for this!</font>

224
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:49,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Demon King Potato Warrior 
unleashed his wrath on me.</i></font>

225
00:10:49,830 --> 00:10:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure he was very upset about 
being turned into a vegetable.</font>

226
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:55,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, he was mad that I gave 
Evil Dragon God Bahalmetia</font>

227
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:57,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">treats until he joined my side.</font>

228
00:10:57,370 --> 00:10:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got him to join your 
party by giving him treats?</font>

229
00:10:59,460 --> 00:11:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, his favorite 
treat was eggplant!</font>

230
00:11:02,050 --> 00:11:04,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that where the cook went?</font>

231
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's also not a big eater.</font>

232
00:11:06,900 --> 00:11:10,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And thus we solve the mystery 
of the half-eaten eggplant.</i></font>

233
00:11:17,980 --> 00:11:21,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Toma-toma-toma-toma-tomato!</font>

234
00:11:22,610 --> 00:11:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Demon King Potatotia's blade 
sliced through space-time itself!</font>

235
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was that, by chance, his real name?</font>

236
00:11:28,950 --> 00:11:32,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, I can see the staff through 
the hole ripped in space-time.</font>

237
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:39,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tofu Martial Artist risked 
his life to stop the blade.</i></font>

238
00:11:39,170 --> 00:11:41,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It cuts space-time but not tofu.</font>

239
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:47,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And so the poor little 
caterpillar became a star!</i></font>

240
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Farewell, Cabbage.</font>

241
00:11:49,210 --> 00:11:50,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were delicious.</font>

242
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:56,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onion Knight told a sad story to make 
the Demon King cry, which blinded him.</font>

243
00:11:56,990 --> 00:11:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think that's how onions 
are supposed to make you cry.</font>

244
00:12:02,590 --> 00:12:06,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And then Evil Dragon God 
Bahalmetia burned everything to ash!</i></font>

245
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:09,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop putting actual powerful 
things in the story. It's weird.</font>

246
00:12:12,910 --> 00:12:15,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take... this!</font>

247
00:12:20,650 --> 00:12:23,300
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font size="40">Vegetable</font></b></font></font>

248
00:12:20,650 --> 00:12:23,300
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font size="10"><font color="#eeece5">Reincarnation Section
Video Production</font></font></b></font></font>

249
00:12:22,370 --> 00:12:23,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With that,</font>

250
00:12:23,300 --> 00:12:27,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Demon King was defeated, 
and peace returned to the land.</font>

251
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But since they didn't want the hero 
to rot, they planted me in a field,</font>

252
00:12:30,790 --> 00:12:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I'm still cultivated to this day 
under the brand name "Hero Tomato!"</font>

253
00:12:36,710 --> 00:12:39,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hence why there's no 
tomato in the gift box.</font>

254
00:12:39,340 --> 00:12:41,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that's right.</font>

255
00:12:41,970 --> 00:12:44,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like your fit is over, huh?</font>

256
00:12:44,850 --> 00:12:46,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do feel like I've calmed down.</font>

257
00:12:46,910 --> 00:12:50,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'll use these 
veggies to make curry.</font>

258
00:12:51,160 --> 00:12:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

259
00:12:53,830 --> 00:12:57,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let us hold one another in our 
arms while we peel onions.</font>

260
00:12:58,940 --> 00:13:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wasn't over!</font>

261
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:10,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always want to annihilate 
myself after these fits.</font>

262
00:13:10,820 --> 00:13:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

263
00:13:13,950 --> 00:13:16,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it safe to come out?</font>

264
00:13:16,190 --> 00:13:17,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My fit is over.</font>

265
00:13:17,910 --> 00:13:20,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me try getting close to make sure!</font>

266
00:13:29,450 --> 00:13:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if you immediately resurrect,</font>

267
00:13:31,730 --> 00:13:35,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's still creepy to see you come back 
without changing your expression at all.</font>

268
00:13:35,690 --> 00:13:38,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I learned a way to not feel pain!</font>

269
00:13:38,370 --> 00:13:41,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kids these days are barely even human.</font>

270
00:13:41,020 --> 00:13:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's almost time for 
another reincarnation!</font>

271
00:13:44,130 --> 00:13:47,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've started saying it yourself, huh?</font>

272
00:13:53,330 --> 00:13:53,350
<font size="20"><font size="8"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#3a241e">The Lock on a Treasure Chest</font></b></font></font></font>

273
00:13:53,350 --> 00:13:53,390
<font size="20"><font size="9"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#3a241e">The Lock on a Treasure Chest</font></b></font></font></font>

274
00:13:53,390 --> 00:13:55,620
<font size="20"><font size="10"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#3a241e">The Lock on a Treasure Chest</font></b></font></font></font>

275
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:55,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The lock on a treasure chest!</font>

276
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Inorganic this time, I see.</font>

277
00:13:57,090 --> 00:13:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's my specialty!</font>

278
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll give you credit for your optimism.</font>

279
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:03,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's give you your options.</font>

280
00:14:03,300 --> 00:14:05,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's add the usual shock trap...</font>

281
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Denied.</font>

282
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:05,690
<font size="20">{\an1}<font color="#4e5b68"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Shock Trap</b></font></font></font>

283
00:14:05,690 --> 00:14:05,780
<font size="20">{\an1}<font color="#4e5b68"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Shock Tr</b></font></font></font>

284
00:14:05,780 --> 00:14:05,860
<font size="20">{\an1}<font color="#4e5b68"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Shock</b></font></font></font>

285
00:14:05,860 --> 00:14:05,940
<font size="20">{\an1}<font color="#4e5b68"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Sho</b></font></font></font>

286
00:14:05,940 --> 00:14:06,050
<font size="20">{\an1}<font color="#4e5b68"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Sh</b></font></font></font>

287
00:14:06,150 --> 00:14:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

288
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How am I supposed to fight, then?</font>

289
00:14:08,980 --> 00:14:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you fighting, again?</font>

290
00:14:10,570 --> 00:14:11,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gloom...</font>

291
00:14:11,690 --> 00:14:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Locks are about defense, not offense.</font>

292
00:14:15,710 --> 00:14:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Act like it.</font>

293
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:23,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do my best to bring back what's 
in the treasure chest as a gift!</font>

294
00:14:24,350 --> 00:14:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just die already...</font>

295
00:14:29,010 --> 00:14:30,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't open.</font>

296
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:33,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm...</font>

297
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:35,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">back!</font>

298
00:14:35,370 --> 00:14:37,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't open the door to the 
safe where I keep all the snacks</font>

299
00:14:37,980 --> 00:14:39,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want you eating.</font>

300
00:14:39,290 --> 00:14:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please open it.</font>

301
00:14:40,340 --> 00:14:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so cold!</font>

302
00:14:42,230 --> 00:14:44,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is our big reunion!</font>

303
00:14:45,980 --> 00:14:47,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's open.</font>

304
00:14:47,750 --> 00:14:49,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your time as a lock paid off.</font>

305
00:14:49,150 --> 00:14:51,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could open the door to your heart, too!</font>

306
00:14:52,350 --> 00:14:55,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All it takes is a smile...!</font>

307
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:04,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's hear your report.</font>

308
00:15:04,910 --> 00:15:09,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I became the lock on the treasure 
chest at the holy temple!</i></font>

309
00:15:09,670 --> 00:15:11,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You look pretty cheap.</i></font>

310
00:15:11,700 --> 00:15:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I cost 20 yen to make!</i></font>

311
00:15:13,230 --> 00:15:14,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That seems too cheap.</i></font>

312
00:15:14,540 --> 00:15:16,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since that's hard to understand, 
if we depict me as a human...</i></font>

313
00:15:17,850 --> 00:15:18,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I look like this.</i></font>

314
00:15:19,470 --> 00:15:22,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As for the key, it was in the next room.</i></font>

315
00:15:22,290 --> 00:15:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was made out of pure gold 
and decorated with jewels!</i></font>

316
00:15:26,330 --> 00:15:28,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So that's where the money went.</i></font>

317
00:15:28,530 --> 00:15:31,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm curious what was inside the chest.</font>

318
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:32,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Demon King!</font>

319
00:15:33,160 --> 00:15:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Demon King was inside the chest.</font>

320
00:15:35,290 --> 00:15:36,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's what it was.</font>

321
00:15:36,950 --> 00:15:39,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How'd they get him in the box?</font>

322
00:15:39,660 --> 00:15:41,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They folded him six times 
and stuffed him in!</font>

323
00:15:41,560 --> 00:15:44,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He must've died when he 
was folded six times.</font>

324
00:15:44,830 --> 00:15:47,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It was a guy named Demon King Spacious!</i></font>

325
00:15:45,270 --> 00:15:50,050
<font size="20"><font size="16">{\an2}<font face="Arial Black"><font color="#050201">Having Plenty of Room</font></font></font></font>

326
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}No nominative determinism here, I see.</i></font>

327
00:15:50,050 --> 00:15:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In the distant past, Demon King 
Spacious tried to destroy the world!</i></font>

328
00:16:02,410 --> 00:16:06,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The humans shall serve beneath my seas!</font>

329
00:16:07,110 --> 00:16:08,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this?!</font>

330
00:16:11,650 --> 00:16:16,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Curse you!</font>

331
00:16:17,860 --> 00:16:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I set it so I would be 
the lock on his chest!</font>

332
00:16:21,250 --> 00:16:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were getting greedy, for a lock.</font>

333
00:16:24,170 --> 00:16:30,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'll get you for this...
I'll get you for this! No matter what!</font>

334
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:30,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He spent every day raging at 
the god who sealed him away!</i></font>

335
00:16:30,570 --> 00:16:32,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sold the game I lent you online!</font>

336
00:16:32,770 --> 00:16:36,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said you'd only eat a bite of 
my ice cream, and you ate it all!</font>

337
00:16:36,430 --> 00:16:37,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who does that?!</font>

338
00:16:37,850 --> 00:16:42,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll forgive you for sowing the seeds of 
eternal war between demons and humanity.</font>

339
00:16:42,140 --> 00:16:45,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'll never forgive 
you for putting lemon</font>

340
00:16:45,370 --> 00:16:47,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">on my chicken wings without asking first!</font>

341
00:16:47,690 --> 00:16:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This god sounds like a real asshole.</font>

342
00:16:51,290 --> 00:16:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I felt so bad for poor Demon King 
Spacious that I talked to him one day.</font>

343
00:16:57,070 --> 00:17:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know it sucks, but eat 
something good and forget it.</font>

344
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:04,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I especially recommend 
delicious sockeye salmon.</font>

345
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:06,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who the hell are you?!</font>

346
00:17:06,270 --> 00:17:09,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare a mere lock speak 
to me, the Demon King!</font>

347
00:17:09,590 --> 00:17:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Know your place!</font>

348
00:17:11,300 --> 00:17:13,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A mere Demon King was being rude to me,</i></font>

349
00:17:13,490 --> 00:17:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so I hit him with a spell that 
sprayed him with lemon juice.</i></font>

350
00:17:15,970 --> 00:17:16,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lemon Juice!</font>

351
00:17:19,710 --> 00:17:21,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lemon! Ahh!</font>

352
00:17:21,810 --> 00:17:23,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My eyes! My eyes!</font>

353
00:17:23,940 --> 00:17:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You were brutal as a lock, too.</i></font>

354
00:17:25,600 --> 00:17:28,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it! Stop pouring lemon juice on me!</font>

355
00:17:31,320 --> 00:17:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this liquid?</font>

356
00:17:35,550 --> 00:17:38,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An ominous portent!</font>

357
00:17:38,990 --> 00:17:41,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is definitely ominous!</font>

358
00:17:42,810 --> 00:17:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I also hit him with a spell that 
filled the box with vegetable oil,</font>

359
00:17:44,810 --> 00:17:49,630
<font size="20"><font color="#060100"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="8">Vegetable Oil</font></b></font></font></font>

360
00:17:46,050 --> 00:17:47,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">perfect for crispy tempura!</font>

361
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:49,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you trying to cook?</font>

362
00:17:52,420 --> 00:17:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grr!</font>

363
00:17:55,920 --> 00:18:00,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Demon King Spacious was a fish monster, 
so this caused him to awaken.</i></font>

364
00:18:00,320 --> 00:18:01,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was oil, not water, though.</i></font>

365
00:18:03,930 --> 00:18:08,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the priests decided he was 
dangerous and put up another barrier.</i></font>

366
00:18:08,830 --> 00:18:10,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be quelled!</font>

367
00:18:10,390 --> 00:18:12,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn you, Demon King!</font>

368
00:18:12,940 --> 00:18:16,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was a barrier that made oil burn...</i></font>

369
00:18:18,630 --> 00:18:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ahh! H-Hot!</font>

370
00:18:36,380 --> 00:18:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is...</font>

371
00:18:37,350 --> 00:18:38,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too ominous!</font>

372
00:18:38,650 --> 00:18:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh no! Oh no! Oh no!</font>

373
00:18:40,490 --> 00:18:41,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

374
00:18:43,100 --> 00:18:46,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Some guy appeared, holding the key.</i></font>

375
00:18:47,310 --> 00:18:50,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's open 'er up.</font>

376
00:18:50,420 --> 00:18:52,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's this guy?</font>

377
00:18:52,460 --> 00:18:55,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The key's huge! Wait, wait, wait!</font>

378
00:18:55,190 --> 00:18:56,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lemon!</font>

379
00:19:02,250 --> 00:19:04,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Key!</font>

380
00:19:05,610 --> 00:19:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make you pay...</font>

381
00:19:15,210 --> 00:19:20,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">None may treat a god like this.</font>

382
00:19:20,010 --> 00:19:21,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the guy was the god?</font>

383
00:19:21,550 --> 00:19:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even sealed, you resist a god?</font>

384
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:28,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Demon King is truly evil!</font>

385
00:19:28,220 --> 00:19:32,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall end your life myself!</font>

386
00:19:33,730 --> 00:19:36,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holy Sword of Banishing Evil!</font>

387
00:19:36,480 --> 00:19:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Annihilate this wicked soul!</font>

388
00:19:40,340 --> 00:19:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He got serious.</i></font>

389
00:19:42,230 --> 00:19:43,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vegetable oil!</font>

390
00:19:45,450 --> 00:19:46,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">God!</font>

391
00:19:48,080 --> 00:19:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Corn oil!</font>

392
00:19:50,200 --> 00:19:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Olive oil!</font>

393
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:00,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Holy Sword of Banishing Evil...</font>

394
00:20:02,890 --> 00:20:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You asshole! You! Asshole!</font>

395
00:20:05,810 --> 00:20:07,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so evil!</font>

396
00:20:10,060 --> 00:20:11,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And then he got shocked.</i></font>

397
00:20:13,230 --> 00:20:15,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I took that off the option list.</font>

398
00:20:15,370 --> 00:20:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The treasure chest itself 
had it as an option.</font>

399
00:20:19,500 --> 00:20:22,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The treasure chest was 
reincarnated too, huh?</font>

400
00:20:22,490 --> 00:20:26,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And down went the god.</i></font>

401
00:20:30,070 --> 00:20:31,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Demon King Spacious went down too.</i></font>

402
00:20:31,790 --> 00:20:33,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He got shocked too, huh?</i></font>

403
00:20:35,080 --> 00:20:39,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And so the hero defeated 
Demon King Spacious.</i></font>

404
00:20:39,120 --> 00:20:41,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The treasure chest was the hero, huh?</i></font>

405
00:20:42,050 --> 00:20:44,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The treasure chest was 
kind of a jerk, huh?</font>

406
00:20:44,990 --> 00:20:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He beat not just the Demon 
King, but the god, too.</font>

407
00:20:47,130 --> 00:20:49,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you were just as responsible.</font>

408
00:20:50,950 --> 00:20:53,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since both the god and the 
Demon King were gone,</i></font>

409
00:20:53,940 --> 00:20:56,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the seeds of discord between the 
demons and humans were gone,</i></font>

410
00:20:56,390 --> 00:20:59,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and the world became peaceful on its own.</i></font>

411
00:20:59,190 --> 00:21:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's a nice ending.</i></font>

412
00:21:01,940 --> 00:21:01,990
<font size="20"><font size="40"><font color="#f0f0c3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>H<font color="#cbc796">e<font color="#8c8c57">r<font color="#484744">o</font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

413
00:21:01,990 --> 00:21:02,030
<font size="20"><font size="38"><font color="#f0f0c3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>H<font color="#cbc796">e<font color="#8c8c57">r<font color="#484744">o</font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

414
00:21:02,030 --> 00:21:02,070
<font size="20"><font size="34"><font color="#f0f0c3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>H<font color="#cbc796">e<font color="#8c8c57">r<font color="#484744">o</font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

415
00:21:02,070 --> 00:21:02,110
<font size="20"><font size="30"><font color="#f0f0c3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>H<font color="#cbc796">e<font color="#8c8c57">r<font color="#484744">o</font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

416
00:21:02,110 --> 00:21:02,150
<font size="20"><font size="28"><font color="#f0f0c3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>H<font color="#cbc796">e<font color="#8c8c57">r<font color="#484744">o</font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

417
00:21:02,150 --> 00:21:02,190
<font size="20"><font size="24"><font color="#f0f0c3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>H<font color="#cbc796">e<font color="#8c8c57">r<font color="#484744">o</font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

418
00:21:02,190 --> 00:21:02,240
<font size="20"><font size="20"><font color="#f0f0c3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>H<font color="#cbc796">e<font color="#8c8c57">r<font color="#484744">o</font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

419
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:02,280
<font size="20"><font size="16"><font color="#f0f0c3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>H<font color="#cbc796">e<font color="#8c8c57">r<font color="#484744">o</font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

420
00:21:02,280 --> 00:21:02,320
<font size="20"><font size="14"><font color="#f0f0c3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>H<font color="#cbc796">e<font color="#8c8c57">r<font color="#484744">o</font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

421
00:21:02,320 --> 00:21:06,160
<font size="20"><font size="12"><font color="#f0f0c3"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>H<font color="#cbc796">e<font color="#8c8c57">r<font color="#484744">o</font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

422
00:21:02,460 --> 00:21:03,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A hero robot?</font>

423
00:21:03,940 --> 00:21:05,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He had a transformation fetish.</font>

424
00:21:07,210 --> 00:21:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}But the guy brought an end 
to my job as a lock...</i></font>

425
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:13,160
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font size="26">Lock on a Treasure Chest</font></b></font></font>

426
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:13,160
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font size="10">Reincarnation Section
Video Production</font></b></font></font>

427
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:13,160
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font size="16">Koji Kumeta</font></b></font></font>

428
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:15,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't get to do anything.</font>

429
00:21:15,580 --> 00:21:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you did a lot, for a lock.</font>

430
00:21:19,580 --> 00:21:22,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, as a gift I brought what 
was in the treasure chest...</font>

431
00:21:22,660 --> 00:21:23,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go put it back.</font>

432
00:21:24,910 --> 00:21:31,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? A great Demon King wants to 
transform into something like that?</font>

433
00:21:32,210 --> 00:21:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that's right.</font>

